# ================================================================== #
# Sandbox - Daytona (CODE EVALUATOR, not the agent runner)
# ================================================================== #
# The CODE EVALUATOR's sandbox (api/services), which runs custom evaluator code. The agent
# runner NEVER reads these bare DAYTONA_* names; it has its own AGENTA_RUNNER_DAYTONA_* set
# under "Agenta - Agent runner" above.
# The key, url, and target may point at the same Daytona account as the agent runner. The
# SNAPSHOT MUST NOT BE SHARED in either direction: this one (for example `daytona-small`) has
# no agent harness installed, so copying it into AGENTA_RUNNER_DAYTONA_SNAPSHOT boots agents
# into an image that cannot run them.
# DAYTONA_API_KEY=
# DAYTONA_API_URL=https://app.daytona.io/api
# DAYTONA_TARGET=eu
# The code evaluator's snapshot.
# DAYTONA_SNAPSHOT_CODE=
# Generic fallback snapshot, used when DAYTONA_SNAPSHOT_CODE is unset.
# DAYTONA_SNAPSHOT=
# NGROK_AUTHTOKEN=

